data.description: Nestled within the charming Old Jefferson subdivision - This exquisite home features 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 well appointed bathrooms - Upon entering, you'll immediately notice the tasteful details throughout the home, including stunning wood floors that lend warmth and character - The kitchen boasts granite countertops, blending style with functionality for all your culinary needs - The master bathroom serves as a tranquil oasis, complete with double sinks and more beautiful granite counters -  With 1,724 square feet of Living Area, this residence offers ample room for you to personalize and make it your own - This property provides an inviting backdrop for creating cherished memories - Don’t wait to make this charming home yours - Measurements and acreage not guaranteed by Realtor or Broker
